Techno-Wizard
The Techno-Wizard has unlocked the secret of fusing magic with technology,
creating devices powered by PPE that blend arcane power with engineering
ingenuity. A Techno-Wizard's creations are unique artifacts on Rifts Earth.

Techno-Wizards begin with both technical skills and magical lore, drawing
from Technical, Mechanical, Electrical, and Lore categories. They maintain
a PPE pool to power their devices and cast spells.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 10.
PPE: Starting PPE pool fuels both spellcasting and device activation.
Flags: [Techno-Wizard] [Magic User]
Starting equipment: Personal workshop tools, one techno-wizard creation of
choice, spellbook, sidearm, and an armoured work coat.
